{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Configure-google-cloud-ssh/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>如果我们需要通过本地的ssh登陆google cloud instance，主要要进行如下几步：</p>\n<p>修改ssh配置文件/etc/ssh/sshd_config</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/ssh/sshd_config</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后把该文件修改为：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">...\nPermitRootLogin yes\n...\n# Change to no to disable tunnelled clear text passwords\nPasswordAuthentication yes\n...</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后给root用话设置密码：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">passwd</span> root</code></pre></div>\n<p>之后重启ssh</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">/etc/init.d/ssh restart</code></pre></div>\n<p>最后在左边的导航栏中的MetaData中的ssh里面加入本机的公钥即可。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Google Cloud 配置 ssh","date":"2019-03-09T22:10:02.000Z","tags":["google-cloud","cloud"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Configure-google-cloud-ssh/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"]}